Excerpt: Tessh Genda Genda Tessh) is a seiy, or voice actor who was born in Okayama Prefecture, Japan on May 20, 1948. He is employed by the talent management firm 81 Produce. When he debuted, he used his real name, Mitsuo Yokoi Yokoi Mitsuo). Because he had experience with ballet, he was known by the nickname "Pirouette Genda."
